[0.000, "o", "[1Cof\u001b[1Ca\u001b[1C\"this\u001b[1Cwill\u001b[1Cbe\u001b[1Cneeded\u001b[1Ceventually\"\u001b[1Cbacklog\u001b[1Citem?\r\r\n\r\r\n\u001b[48;2;55;55;55m\u001b[38;2;80;80;80m❯ \u001b[38;2;255;255;255mThe latter - building toward the Phase 3 coordination layer from the roadmap. We need push-based updates rather than polling.\u001b[39m  \u001b[49m\r\r\n\r\r\n\u001b[38;2;255;255;255m⏺\u001b[1C\u001b[39mGood\u001b[1Csignal\u001b[1C—\u001b[1Cthis\u001b[1Cis\u001b[1Cpull-forward\u001b[1Cwork\u001b[1Cfor\u001b[1CPhase\u001b[1C3,\u001b[1Cand\u001b[1Cthe\u001b[1Cpolling-vs-push\u001b[1Cdistinction\u001b[1Cis\u001b[1Ca\u001b[1Creal\u001b[1Carchitectural\u001b[1Cinflection\r\r\n\u001b[2Cpoint.\r\r\n\r\r\n\u001b[2CNext\u001b[1Cprobe:\r\r\n\r\r\n\u001b[2C\u001b[1mScope\u001b[1Csniff\u001b[1C\u001b[22m—\u001b[1CGut\u001b[1Cfeel:\u001b[1Chours,\u001b[1Cdays,\u001b[1Cor\u001b[1Cweeks?\u001b[1C(Not\u001b[1Ca\u001b[1Ccommitment\u001b[1C—\u001b[1Cjust\u001b[1Ccalibration.)\r\r\n\r\r\n\u001b[48;2;55;55;55m\u001b[38;2;80;80;80m❯ \u001b[38;2;255;255;255mI think we can start small - support GH/ADO webhooks - but plan for other types if they differ. Couple weeks.\u001b[39m                  \u001b[49m\r\r\n\r\r\n\u001b[38;2;255;255;255m⏺\u001b[1C\u001b[39mCouple\u001b[1Cweeks,\u001b[1CGH/ADO\u001b[1Cfirst,\u001b[1Cextensible\u001b[1Cby\u001b[1Cdesign.\u001b[1CThat's\u001b[1Ca\u001b[1Creasonable\u001b[1Cscope.\r\r\n\r"]
